Drop Ship: Follow provided instructions
  and navigate ship to center of pipe
       when in DCS Ranging mode.

 During rescue missions, watch your men
  Their screens indicate their status.

1, 2, 3, 4 * * * * * * * *Switch Marine
Joystick * * * * * * * * * * * Movement
Button * * * * * * * * * * * * * * Fire
 When there are two or more marines on
screen at one time, they should be safe
from attack or able to free each other.

  Operations room rampage: Use fire to
 push the aliens back until you escape.

  Maze: Press fire to blow up marine.

  Each mission will provide a continue
 (status) code so best write them down.
Return * * * * * *Advance to next level
CTRL+Q then Space * * * * *Replay level
